title: Tesla’s Full Self Driving Rollout with Quinn from Snazzy Labs
description:
This week Marques and Andrew talk about the new Amazon Astro robot for a bit before getting Quinn from Snazzy Labs on the phone to dig deep into the Tesla FSD beta rollout. they also talk about the new Rivian R1T that Quinn got to drive. It's a fun one!
